    "causal_summary": "This specification defines a comprehensive restructuring of the SpecKit template system from monolithic templates to a CORE + ADDENDUM compositional architecture. The optimization addresses three critical issues: template bloat from unused sections, lack of meaningful differentiation between levels, and absence of parallel sub-agent support for spec creation.",
